text: Amblymora rufula is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1950. It is known from Malaysia.BioLib.cz - Amblymora rufula. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Amblymora Category:Beetles described in 1950
